title: PlayStation State of Play Incoming! - Kinda Funny Games Daily 03.08.22
description:
Gary and Greg jump into predictions for tomorrow's PlayStation State of Play, Ukraine charities, and more!

Time Stamps - 
00:00:00 - Start
00:09:55 - Housekeeping
Project HOPE tomorrow stream
PSILY is live – has been PS GOTY been locked?

00:42:00 - GTA Online Deets

01:03:25 - Out today

Tomorrow’s Hosts:Janet and Tim
